{"title_page": "Ex on the Beach (British series 11)", "text_new": "{{Short description|Eleventh series of Ex on the Beach}}\n{{Use dmy dates|date=September 2015}}\n{{Use British English|date=September 2015}}\n{{Infobox television season\n| bgcolour             = #2CB46C\n| image                = \n| caption              = \n| country              = [[United Kingdom]]\n| network              = [[MTV (UK and Ireland)|MTV]]\n| first_aired          = {{Start date|2020|01|21|df=y}}\n| last_aired           = {{End date|present|df=y}}\n| num_episodes         =\n| prev_series          = [[Ex on the Beach (British series 9)|Series 9]]\n| next_series          = \n| season_number        = 11\n| image_alt            = \n| starring             = \n| released             = \n| episode_list         = \n}}\n\nThe '''eleventh series''' of ''[[Ex on the Beach]]'' began airing on 21 January 2020 with a 90-minute special.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/reality-tv/a30162203/celebrity-ex-on-the-beach-line-up-mtv-2020-joey-essex-calum-best/|title=Celebrity Ex on the Beach confirms Joey Essex and Love Island's Georgia Harrison on official line-up|first=Chris|last=Edwards|date=9 December 2019|work=[[Digital Spy]]}}</ref> This series is billed as ''\"Celebrity Ex on the Beach\"'' as for the first time, it features a set of famous cast members. The series was filmed in [[Marbella]].\n\nThe series follows the cancellation of the tenth series, which was set to air in early 2019, which was cancelled due to the death of cast member [[Mike Thalassitis]].<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.ohmymag.co.uk/love-island/the-next-series-of-ex-on-the-beach-has-been-cancelled-following-mike-thalassitis-death_art3561.html|title=The Next Series Of Ex On The Beach Has Been Cancelled Following Mike Thalassitis' Death|date=20 March 2019|work=Oh My|language=en|access-date=22 January 2020}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.digitalspy.com/tv/reality-tv/a26880794/ex-on-the-beach-series-10-mike-thalassitis-pulled-from-air/|title=Ex on the Beach's new series pulled by MTV after Mike Thalassitis death|last=Houghton|first=Rianne|date=20 March 2019|work=[[Digital Spy]]|language=en|access-date=22 January 2020}}</ref> None of the other cast members for the tenth series were announced.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://metro.co.uk/2019/07/17/mtvs-ex-beach-set-return-year-season-10-pulled-wake-love-island-star-mike-thalassitis-death-10379143/|title=Ex On The Beach 'set to return this year' after Mike Thalassitis death|last=Deen|first=Sarah|access-date=8 August 2019|work=[[Metro (British newspaper)|Metro]]}}</ref>\n\n==Cast==\nThe list of celebrity cast members was released on 9 December 2019.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://tellymix.co.uk/reality-tv/ex-on-the-beach/414121-ex-on-the-beach-2020-cast-season-11-start-date.html|title=Celebrity Ex On The Beach cast and start date confirmed for 2020|first=Josh|last=Darvill|date=22 December 2019|work=TellyMix}}</ref> They include four men; Olympic athlete [[Ashley McKenzie]], television personality [[Calum Best]], ''[[The Only Way Is Essex]]'' star [[Joey Essex]], and ''[[Love Island (2015 TV series, series 5)|Love Island]]'' star Michael Griffiths, and four women; ''Love Island'' star Georgia Harrison, ''[[The Valleys (TV series)|The Valleys]]'' star [[Lateysha Grace]], playboy model [[Lorena Medina]] and ''[[Mob Wives]]'' star Marissa Jade.<ref>{{Cite news|url=https://www.realitytitbit.com/whats-on/meet-the-celebrity-ex-on-the-beach-2020-cast-ashley-mckenzie-to-michael-griffiths|title=Meet the Celebrity Ex on the Beach 2020 cast: Ashley McKenzie to Michael Griffiths!|date=10 December 2019}}</ref> It was also announced that the exes joining the series would be celebrities.\n\nEllie Brown, star of the [[Love Island (2015 TV series, series 4)|fourth series]] of ''Love Island'' was the first ex to arrive, hoping to rekindle a relationship with Essex, her ex-boyfriend.\n\n*'''Bold''' indicates original cast member; all other cast were brought into the series as an ex.\n\n{| class=\"wikitable sortable\"\n|-\n! Episodes !! Name !! Age (at start of series) !! Notability !! Exes\n|-\n| 12\n| '''[[Ashley McKenzie]]'''\n| 30\n| Olympian\n| Danielle Kedward\n|-\n| 12\n| '''[[Calum Best]]'''\n| 38\n| TV personality\n| Ayesha Reid, Marissa Jade, Megan Rapley, Victoria Winterford\n|-\n| 12\n| '''Georgia Harrison'''\n| 24\n| ''[[Love Island (2015 TV series, series 3)|Love Island]]'' star\n| Miles Nazaire\n|-\n| 12\n| '''[[Joey Essex]]'''\n| 29\n| ''[[The Only Way Is Essex]]'' star\n| Ellie Brown\n|-\n| 12\n| '''[[Lateysha Grace]]'''\n| 26\n| ''[[The Valleys (TV series)|The Valleys]]'' star\n| {{n/a}}\n|-\n| 12\n| '''[[Lorena Medina]]'''\n| 27\n| Model\n| Itay Ohayon, Patrick Hale\n|-\n| 12\n| '''[[Marissa Jade]]'''\n| 34\n| ''[[Mob Wives]]'' star\n| Calum Best\n|-\n| 12\n| '''Michael Griffiths'''\n| 27\n| ''[[Love Island (2015 TV series, series 5)|Love Island]]'' star\n| {{n/a}}\n|-\n! style=\"background:#000;\" colspan=\"6\"|\n|-\n| 12\n| Ellie Brown\n| 21\n| ''[[Love Island (2015 TV series, series 4)|Love Island]]'' star\n| Charlie Brake, Joey Essex\n|-\n| 11\n| [[David McIntosh (Gladiators)|David McIntosh]]\n| 34\n| Media personality\n| Metisha Schaefer, Tiffany Pollard\n|-\n|-\n| 8\n| Victoria Winterford\n| 26\n| ''[[Celebs Go Dating (series 3)|Celebs Go Dating]]'' star\n| Calum Best, Lotan Carter \n|-\n|-\n| 3\n| Itay Ohayon\n| 26\n| Model\n| Lorena Medina\n|-\n|-\n| 4\n| Danielle Kedward\n| 29\n| Glamour model\n| Ashley McKenzie\n|-\n|-\n| 4\n| Charlie Brake\n| 24\n| ''[[Love Island (2015 TV series, series 4)|Love Island]]'' star\n| Ellie Brown\n|-\n|-\n| 7\n| Sophie Kasaei\n| 30\n| ''[[Geordie Shore]]'' star\n| {{n/a}}\n|-\n| 5\n| [[Tiffany Pollard]]\n| 38\n| TV personality\n| David McIntosh\n|-\n| 3\n| Lotan Carter\n| 30\n| ''[[Big Brother (British series 18)|Big Brother]]'' star\n| Victoria Winterford\n|-\n| 4\n| Patrick Hale\n| 20\n| Model and Singer\n| Lorena Medina\n|-\n| 1\n| Ayesha Reid\n| 26